106
00:06:37,120 --> 00:06:38,890
Saya tiba-tiba berasa sangat sejuk.

107
00:06:41,390 --> 00:06:43,296
Feng Qi berkata beberapa perkara yang pelik

108
00:06:43,320 --> 00:06:44,740
