109
00:06:45,030 --> 00:06:48,010
Sesuatu tentang saya pernah ke sini sebelum ini.

110
00:06:50,390 --> 00:06:51,390
Saya akan mencari dia.

111
00:06:53,520 --> 00:06:54,520
apa salahnya

112
00:06:56,590 --> 00:06:58,100
Awak nampak tak sihat.

113
