213
00:12:39,630 --> 00:12:43,180
Ketika itu, You Chi takut akan kuasa ayah saya

214
00:12:44,280 --> 00:12:45,280
dan berkomplot terhadapnya,

215
00:12:46,040 --> 00:12:49,420
